Place the peach into the right side of the sink.
Turn right, walk slightly over to the fridge.
Open the doors of the refrigerator, take out the peach from the bottom shelf, and close the door.
Walk over to the kitchen counter near the sink.
Put the peach behind the other one in the kitchen sink.
